@Node Register "Registering HBBS"

  Registering HBBS
  ================

    I was going to make this program free, but I had to buy a load of
    development software and hardware and systems to test it on which
    has cost me a small fortune.

    Because of this outragous expenditure HBBS will become shareware.

    I am relying or your goodwill to register this program if you use it.

    If you can't be bothered to register then I can't be bothered to give
    you cool software which I know everyone will be using!

    If you like HBBS and use it to run a BBS then you must register this
    program.  I'm not out to make money from this software, it'll just
    encorage me to continue developing it and cover my cost of hardware
    upgrades, phone bills and test equiment.

    It only costs Ł25 UK Pounds no matter where you live.

    If you live outside the UK, cash or international money orders are the
    only form of payment that I can accept.  It can be sent to me in
    US dollars or DM, as long as it works out at 30 UK Pounds sterling
    (The extra Ł5 covers conversion to back from US$/DM to UK Pounds)

    Anyway, that said, send the registration fee:

      Dominic Clifton
      9 Shires Copse
      Southbourne
      Bournemouth
      Dorset
      BH6 4AL
      England.

    If you are sending a cheque or I.M.O. then make it payable to D. Clifton.

    Remember to include a return name, address and telephone number and
    e-mail address!

    If you have already bought a BBS system and are switching to HBBS and you
    provide me with a receipt and photocopy of your license agreement then
    you qualify for a Ł5 UK Pound discount!

    When you register you will receive:

    * HydraBBS CD-Rom with the full source code

    * serial number

    * key file

    * User and password for your private area on the web-site

    * Tech support telephone number

    So register NOW!

@EndNode


